TI Caregiver burden after stroke: towards a structural model
SO NEUROLOGIA I NEUROCHIRURGIA POLSKA
LA English
DT Article
DE burden; caregiver; stroke
ID QUALITY-OF-LIFE; INFORMAL CAREGIVERS; DEPRESSIVE SYMPTOMS; COHERENCE;
